text:
[01:58.67]不是在开玩笑…吗？
[02:03.80]是…吗
[02:08.41]嗯 是啊
[02:15.21]其实我也变得有奇怪的感觉了
[02:24.34]那个…对不起
[02:27.88]我完全没有这方面的知识
[02:31.93]从哪里开始才好呢？
[02:36.65]我知道了 稍等 我离开一下
[02:43.57]诶 不能开摄像头 因为太羞耻了
[02:52.22]好了哦 睡衣的前面 解开了
trans:
[01:58.67] Are you not joking…?
[02:03.80] Are you…?
[02:08.41] Yeah, I am.
[02:15.21] Actually, I’m starting to feel a bit strange too.
[02:24.34] Um… sorry.
[02:27.88] I don’t know anything about this at all.
[02:31.93] Where should I even start?
[02:36.65] Got it. Wait a moment, I’ll step away for a bit.
[02:43.57] Huh? I can’t turn on the camera—it’s too embarrassing.
[02:52.22] Alright, I’ve unbuttoned the front of my pajamas.
